"{\"uid\": \"thetab.com-2024-08-14-imane-khelif-names-jk-rowling-and-elon-musk-in-lawsuit-heres-what-it-could-mean-for-them\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Olympic gold medal winning boxer is suing those she complains repeatedly and falsely called her a man online  Imane Khelif has filed her cyberbullying lawsuit after she was relentlessly and falsely called a man on social media - specifically Twitter / X - whilst she competed in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The details have been revealed by Imane Khelif's attorney in Paris, who has shared toVarietythat JK Rowling and Elon Musk have both been named in a criminal complaint filed to French authorities over alleged \\\"acts of aggravated cyber harassment\\\" against Algerian boxer and newly crowned Olympic champion Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999083711415, \"rank\": 9.16287171037805e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", 