\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nabil Boudi, Khelif's Paris attorney, has explained that the lawsuit is filed against X itself, which \\\"ensure[s] that the 'prosecution has all the latitude to be able to investigate against all people,\\\" including anyone hiding behind a fake name or an anonymous account - to make sure that everyone can be investigated for any cyber attack on Khelif and her gender.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999083711415, \"rank\": 9.16287171037805e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee backed Imane Khelif fully when she found herself in a huge controversy that saw prominent figures like JK Rowling, Elon Musk and Donald Trump claim she was a man.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.999999524232066, \"rank\": 4.583933148695264e-07, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said \\\"scientifically, this is not a man fighting a woman\\\" and it has been proven that she was born female, and does not identify as intersex as others have claimed.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4786147842017692e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JK Rowling posted a picture of Imane Khelif after her defeat of Italian boxer Angela Carini to her millions of followers saying Khelif was \\\"enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head.\\\"\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 1586, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9983387611432248, \"rank\": 0.0008577333158220902, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what does this Imane Khelif lawsuit mean for those prominent figures like JK Rowling who are not French residents?\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1839, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9564294764628705, \"rank\": 0.04539112764537064, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boudi explained that the lawsuit could have international implications for those outside France, explain